Frendilainen
==============================================================================

Track your facebook friends list.
Requires git and ssmtp.

1) Acquire a long-lived Facebook Graph API access token
    - request 'offline_access' permissions
    - see: http://developers.facebook.com/docs/authentication/

2) Paste it into a file named access_token.txt in this directory
3) Enter the email address you want to notify into a file named email.txt

4) Run the ./init.sh script from within this directory.
5) Set up a cron job. e.g:

# 15 20 * * * konker /home/konker/WORKING/friendilainen/friendilainen

